# What to do

Always run eslint after any changes.
After all changes, review the code and do refactoring if needed.
After all changes, write or update test file and run test with 'npm run test:run'.
After all changes, review that there are duplicated code and refactor it.

Never run development server without my instruction.
Commit message should be in Korean and with 'conventional commits' style.
Never commit without my instruction.

use es-toolkit to improve its readability and performance.
